<p><strong>All metric values on WikiRate must be traced back to a source.</strong></p><p>A source is generally a company report, including CSR Report, Sustainability Report, Annual Report or Integrated Report. It could also be a news article, website, conflict mineral report or modern slavery report and so on. A source can be added to WikiRate as a URL, file upload or report. Once a source is added it will remain of the platform so researchers can easily access the document.</p><p>{{source|add_button}}</p>
